@startuml Seq-00 Happy Path Overview

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline
skinparam noteBorderColor #999999
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7

actor       "Driver"            as Driver
participant "API Gateway"       as GW
participant "Search Service"    as Search
participant "Reservation Svc"   as Reservation
participant "Payment Gateway"   as PGW
participant "Presence Service"  as Presence
participant "Billing Service"   as Billing
participant "Notification Svc"  as Notification

== 1. View Availability ==

Driver -> GW : GET /availability?vehicle_type=CAR
GW -> Search : GetAvailability(vehicle_type)
Search --> GW : { total_available=23, floors[] }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK — "23 spots available"

Driver -> GW : GET /spots?floor_number=2&vehicle_type=CAR
GW -> Search : ListSpots(floor=2, vehicle_type)
Search --> GW : { spots=[A1=AVAILABLE, A2=LOCKED, A3=AVAILABLE, ...] }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK — floor map with spot statuses

== 2. Reserve a Spot ==

note over Driver : Driver picks spot A3 (USER_SELECTED)\nor skips browsing (SYSTEM_ASSIGNED)

Driver -> GW : POST /reservations\n{ idempotency_key, driver_id, vehicle_type, mode, [spot_id] }
GW -> Reservation : CreateReservation(request)
note over Reservation : Acquire Redis lock → verify spot AVAILABLE\n→ INSERT reservation + UPDATE spot=LOCKED\n→ release lock (single DB transaction)
Reservation -> PGW : Create QRIS payment (booking fee 5,000 IDR)
PGW --> Reservation : qr_code_url
Reservation --> GW : { reservation_id, spot_code, qr_code_url,\n  status=PENDING_PAYMENT }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK

== 3. Pay Booking Fee ==

Driver -> PGW : Scan QR & pay 5,000 IDR
PGW --> Reservation : Webhook: payment SUCCESS
note over Reservation : reservation → CONFIRMED\nexpires_at = now() + 1 hour
Notification --> Driver : Push: "Reservation confirmed. Booking fee paid."

== 4. Check In ==

note over Driver : Driver arrives at parking lot\nand taps "Check In" in app

Driver -> GW : POST /sessions/checkin\n{ reservation_id, driver_id }
GW -> Presence : CheckIn(reservation_id, driver_id)
note over Presence : Validate reservation=CONFIRMED & not expired\n→ CREATE session (status=ACTIVE)\n→ reservation → CHECKED_IN
Presence --> GW : { session_id, checked_in_at, status=ACTIVE }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK — session started

== 5. Check Out ==

note over Driver : Driver finishes parking\nand taps "Check Out" in app

Driver -> GW : POST /sessions/checkout\n{ session_id, driver_id }
GW -> Presence : CheckOut(session_id, driver_id)
note over Presence : session → COMPLETED\nreservation → COMPLETED\nspot → AVAILABLE immediately
Presence -> Billing : CalculateAndCreateInvoice(\n  session_id, checked_in_at, checked_out_at)
note over Billing : parking_fee = ceil(hours) × 5,000\novernight_fee = 20,000 if crosses midnight\ntotal = booking_fee + parking_fee + overnight_fee
Billing -> PGW : Create QRIS payment (parking fee)
PGW --> Billing : qr_code_url
Billing --> Presence : { invoice_id, total_idr, qr_code_url }
Presence --> GW : { invoice_id, total_idr, qr_code_url }
GW --> Driver : 200 OK — "Total: 20,000 IDR. Scan to pay."

== 6. Pay Parking Fee ==

Driver -> PGW : Scan QR & pay parking fee
PGW --> Billing : Webhook: payment SUCCESS
note over Billing : invoice → PAID
Notification --> Driver : Push: "Payment received. Thank you for parking!"

@enduml
